Palʊla Giuseppe Verdi kɛ aloma fenaɣ kɩyakʊ hiu ŋgʊ pɩnaɣ 1813 kɛ Rɔnkɔlɩ tɛtʊ taa, Fransɩ kewiyaɣ alɩwaatʊ taa. Ɛsɩba kɔlaɣ fenaɣ 27 wiye pɩnaɣ 1901, Miilaŋ tɛtʊ taa kɛ Itaalii ɛjaɖɛ taa. Ɛ-lʊlʊʊ takayaɣ yɔɔ lɛ, payaɣ-ɩ se Giuseppe Fortunino Francesco Verdi. Payaɣ ɛ-caa se Joseph Fortunin François Verdi Charles nɛ ɛkɛ agɔma ɖɩsɩ taa tʊmɩyɛ laɖʊ nɛ e-ɖoo kɔyɔ Louise Uttini, ɛlɛ kɛ pɩzatʊ tɔyʊ.
[[File:Va, pensiero.jpg|thumb|Va, pensiero]]

Ɛkɛ wendu luɖu nɛ cɩmɩŋ maɖʊ sɔsɔ nɔɔyʋ. Ɛwɛ Itaalii ɛjaɖɛ ɛjaɖɛ taa kɛ cɩmɩŋ yɔɔ maɣzɩm lɩzʋʋ tʋmɩyɛ taa. Cɩmɩŋ maɖʋ sɔsɔ ɛnɛ, ɛ-hɩɖɛ sɛ pɩdɩɩfɛyɩ kpaɣ ɖooo pɩnzɩ mɩnɩŋ XIX taa. Ɛ-kpaɖaʊ taa ɛnɛ cɩmɩŋ maɖaa nɛ wendu teya mba  pɛkpɛnda nɛ pala tʊma yɔ,  nabɛyɛ hɩla yɔ : Bellini, Donizetti,  Puccini nɛ Rossini
[[File:Giuseppe_Verdi_1879_Vanity_Fair_illustration_by_Théobald_Chartran.jpg|thumb|Giuseppe_Verdi_1879_Vanity_Fair_illustration_by_Théobald_Chartran.jpg]]

Pɩnzɩ nzɩ sɩ-taa ɛkɩla ɛ-tʊma labʊ yɔ, nzɩ lɛ kpaɣ pɩnzɩ 1835 nɛ  1901 sɩ-taa.  Ɛ-wɩlɩyaa kɔyɔ: Ferdinando Provesi, Vincenzo nɛ Lavigna. Ɛ-halaa kɔyɔ: Margherita Barezzi nɛ Giuseppina Strepponi.

